Package edu.monash.fit2099.buyers

Class Buyer

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.buyers.Buyer
public class Buyer extends Object
this class is responsible for getting the buyer info that will turn into a buyer object it consists of these private attributes: buyerID: a user made ID that is attached to any given buyer giveName: the buyer's given name familyName: the buyer's family name

      public static Buyer getInstance​(String buyerID, String givenName, String familyName)
